%F A080075 a(n+1) = a(n) + 2^round(L(n)/2), where L(n) is the number of binary digits of a(n); equivalently, floor(log_2(a(n))/2 + 1) in the exponent. [Lemma 2.2 in Borsos et al.] - _M. F. Hasler_, Jul 07 2022
